{
  "stem": "10699.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They had taken everything away from us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In, in no time, we were not anymore the same person.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we kept on crying.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It didn't help very much.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then they, they, they made us walk into a barrack, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know how many we were-- several hundred.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We get into these-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] not beds, the--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--bunks, wooden bunks, with one blanket for four or five or six, I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were so dejected, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the next thing we knew, we, we asked questions.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We tried to get an answer from the so-called other inmates, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I only knew that the next day, when we were on the-- on the Appell, on the call-- 'roll call,' they call it, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] right away, the beatings started, you know, people who couldn't stand, who were too tired-- tired, or who were not behaving according to what the, the system there.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we were-- the only thing we were given, really, was-- in a-- in a-- a, a tin container, there was some kind of water with something in it.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But, you see, it had to pass from the-- from the beginning to the end.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So if you were in the middle, if-- whatever they add, you got one sip or two.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that was your lot.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Whatever it was-- it was just water for us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The only thing I remember quite, quite clearly was some people [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] did get in with their mothers, you know.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
